{
  "tag": "layout-fit",
  "className": "padding10 h100 overflow-auto",
  "initStore": {
    "apiList": [
      {
        "code": "tag",
        "name": "tabs",
        "type": "string",
        "description": "标签页"
      },
      {
        "code": "action",
        "name": "标签页切换动作",
        "type": "array[action]",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "code": "activeKey",
        "name": "当前激活的标签",
        "type": "string",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "code": "items",
        "name": "tab 项的内容",
        "type": "array[configNode]",
        "description": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "tag": "h1",
      "className": "border-bottom",
      "children": "tabs示例"
    },
    {
      "tag": "label",
      "className": "padding-left10 padding-bottom10",
      "children": [
        "Tag=tabs 作为 Ant Design 标签页组件的继承者，确实提供了更多的自定义功能，使得用户可以根据自己的需求来定制标签页的显示效果和行为。以下是一些可能的额外功能和自定义选项。",

        {
          "tag": "a",
          "target": "_blank",
          "href": "https://ant.design/components/tabs-cn",
          "children": "查看tabs文档"
        },
        {
          "tag": "ul",
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "li",
              "children": [
                {
                  "tag": "strong",
                  "children": "功能描述"
                },
                "：tag=tabs 标签确实继承了 Ant Design 标签页的丰富特性，这使得它在设计和功能上都具有很高的灵活性和实用性。Ant Design 是一个基于 React 的 UI 组件库，它提供了一系列高质量的组件"
              ]
            },
            {
              "tag": "li",
              "children": [
                {
                  "tag": "strong",
                  "children": "注意事项"
                },
                "：tab 标签页请求数据，不要进来就将所有标签的数据加载，尽量保持当前激活标签数据加载。可以通过标签页切换，action，刷新数据"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tag": "row",
      "children": [
        {
          "tag": "col",
          "span": 12,
          "style": {
            "height": "400px",
            "overflow": "auto"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "h3",
              "children": "代码配置示例",
              "className": "border-bottom"
            },
            {
              "tag": "coder",
              "language": "json",
              "value":  {
                "style": {
                  "paddingTop": 10
                },
                "tag": "tabs",
                "size": "small",
                "type": "card",
                "action": [
                  {
                    "tag": "reload-init-action",
                    "group": "${activeKey=='user'?'user-list':'ldap-list'}",
                    "description": "页面初始化请求"
                  }
                ],
                "activeKey": "${activeKey}",
                "items": [
                  {
                    "label": "用户管理",
                    "key": "user",
                    "children": [
                      "用户管理内容"
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "label": "ldap分组管理",
                    "key": "ldap",
                    "children": [
                      "ldap 分组内容"
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }

            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tag": "col",
          "span": 12,
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "h3",
              "children": "配置简述",
              "className": "border-bottom"
            },
            {
              "tag": "ol",
              "children": [
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": "tag=tabs-标签页"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": "action-切换标签页后的动作"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": [{
                    "tag": "a",
                    "target": "_blank",
                    "href": "https://ant.design/components/tabs-cn",
                    "children": "查看tabs文档"
                  }]
                }

              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tag": "h3",
      "className": "border-bottom",
      "children": "API（注意：configNode表示低代码配置，action表示动作配置）"
    },
    {
      "tag": "row",
      "children": [
        {
          "tag": "layout-fit",
          "style": {
            "height": "300px",
            "width": "100%"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "table",
              "rowData": "${apiList}",
              "tooltipShowDelay": 0,
              "columnDefs": [
                {
                  "headerName": "#",
                  "width": 60,
                  "suppressSizeToFit": true,
                  "valueGetter": "node.rowIndex + 1",
                  "sortable": false,
                  "pinned": "left"
                },
                {
                  "headerName": "字段",
                  "field": "code",
                  "width": 250,
                  "suppressSizeToFit": true
                },
                {
                  "headerName": "名称",
                  "field": "name",
                  "width": 150,
                  "suppressSizeToFit": true
                },
                {
                  "headerName": "类型",
                  "field": "type",
                  "width": 150,
                  "suppressSizeToFit": true
                },
                {
                  "headerName": "描述",
                  "field": "description",
                  "tooltipField": "description"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tag": "h3",
      "className": "border-bottom",
      "children": "展示示例"
    },
    {
      "tag": "row",
      "children": [

        {
          "tag": "col",
          "span": 16,
          "style": {
            "height": "500px"
          },
          "className": "padding10",
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "label",
              "className": "bold",
              "children": "标签页"
            },
            {
              "tag": "coder-preview",
              "coder": {
                "style": {
                  "paddingTop": 10
                },
                "tag": "tabs",
                "size": "small",
                "type": "card",
                "action": [
                  {
                    "tag": "reload-init-action",
                    "group": "${activeKey=='user'?'user-list':'ldap-list'}",
                    "description": "切换标签页后的动作"
                  }
                ],
                "items": [
                  {
                    "label": "用户管理",
                    "key": "user",
                    "children": [
                      "用户管理内容"
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "label": "ldap分组管理",
                    "key": "ldap",
                    "children": [
                      "ldap 管理内容"
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}